                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Governor <persName type="from">Foster</persName> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Adee</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Baton Rouge, La.</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1899-08-02">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 2, 1899</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I have wired the sheriff of Madison, requesting him to furnish me the evidence
                    confirming his statement on the naturalization of the three Italians, and will
                    forward his reply as soon as received.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Murphy J. Foster</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Governor</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
